{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583340/extras/map.png?t=1737398371\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Bunch of levels!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Diverse map with countless levels, each featuring unique environments, game modes, and powerful upgrades. Replay each level countless of times, with different needed constructions. Explore, conquer, and adapt to become the ultimate road-building master! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583340/extras/Towers.gif?t=1737398371\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unleash the Roadmaster within!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Build your bustling city, navigate traffic chaos, and ensure smooth journeys while racing against the clock for a thriving metropolis. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583340/extras/road_placing_night.gif?t=1737398371\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Hexarium we tried to create a simple and pleasant to the eye stratagy game that revolves around traffic. Don't let the traffic stop no matter what! Or elese? Well, you lose! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2583340/extras/complex.gif?t=1737398371\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Your journey begins here!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you master the art of traffic flow while maintaining a thriving economy? Do you need more bridges, faster roads, or additional markets? Will you be able to control the chaos as it keeps on expanding? It's going to be a challenging journey, but nothing beats the satisfaction of watching your bustling city flourish every second with more and more traf